  {
   cat << EOS
Usage: ngram [OPTION] [STRING]
Displays the N-gram of the passed string.

Option:
  -h, --help          Show usage
  -v, --version       Show version and info

TL;DR
  $ ngram é«˜é ˆã‚¯ãƒªãƒ‹ãƒƒã‚¯
